Deprecated Methods
org.eclipse.stardust.common.error.WorkflowException.getRootCause()
          use WorkflowException.getCause() instead This method returns the inner throwable which caused this workflow exception. In case that the inner exception is no instance of PublicException the returned inner exception will be wrapped in a PublicException instance.
